{"tid":2006734,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"獲欽點三廠與HKRITA密切","createTime":"2020-05-08T03:47:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-08T03:47:01.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2d175df88e972d2045685d813bdc382a69549952","tid":2006734,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T03:47:01.000Z","msg":"全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200508/2D6TNM6SV5ULGZPWJKYVIZS7OQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200508%2F2D6TNM6SV5ULGZPWJKYVIZS7OQ%2F&d=kJsi%2B77Adq7yP7dZlTZe0P3PLjr3aI%2Bxco%2FW%2FCjCBac%3D&h=f1f3b782\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200508%2F2D6TNM6SV5ULGZPWJKYVIZS7OQ%2F&h=be7863f0\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200508/2D6TNM6SV5ULGZPWJKYVIZS7OQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n獲欽點三廠與HKRITA密切<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200508/large/1588870102_d394.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200508%2Flarge%2F1588870102_d394.gif&h=95fd7e89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n口罩在龍達廠房經臭氧消毒儀器消毒後再包裝。馬泉崇攝<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】創科局昨披露Cu Mask的生產商主力是晶苑國際集團，又披露聯業製衣及龍達紡織亦有份參與。翻查資料，3間公司均與今次被政府欽點負責Cu Mask的香港紡織及成衣研發中心（HKRITA）有關連，晶苑集團執行董事王志輝及聯業製衣副總裁蕭毓然同為HKRITA董事；龍達紡織。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：高官倘誤導公眾屬行為失當<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n兩廠高層任中心董事<br />\n<br />\n晶苑國際集團由已故「針織大王」羅定邦的長子羅樂風及其妻蔡玉清在70年代成立，行政總裁為羅樂風兒子羅。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200508/large/1588870105_ff54.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200508%2Flarge%2F1588870105_ff54.gif&h=09eb7f08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n至於另外兩間公司，亦為本港歷史悠久的紡織製衣公司。為口罩提供消毒無塵室做臭氧消毒的龍達紡織，由「香港毛紡大。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n聯業製衣1949年在港成立，在香港、中國及東南亞設製衣廠，公司主席李乃熺曾任HKRITA董事局主席。紡織及製衣界向。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n■記者伍雅謙"}]}